            <title>[HBASE-8697] HBase MapReduce client should be able to retry if Scanner time out</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-8697</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, ScannerTimeOutException is not retried if it occurred in HBase client since it&apos;s derived from DoNotRetryException. We need to provide the mechanism to let user enable/config how to retry in this case when accessing HBase table rows using hadoop.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
